snippet.title: Gems of Magic: Father's Day | Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Remove all obstacles and reunite father and son in 100 challenging levels! In this exciting and adventurous match-3 based puzzle game you will have lots of fun!

Available for pre-order: July 16th 2021
Release date: August 6th 2021
